OL,3,CSecurity firm 'saddened' by deaths of
OL,4,CBritish aid workers killed in air
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FA Dorset-based security firm says it
OL,8,Ffeels "raw and saddened" at the death
OL,9,Fof three British aid workers who were
OL,10,Fkilled in an Israeli air strike in
OL,11,FGaza.
OL,13,FJohn Chapman, 57, James "Jim"
OL,14,FHenderson, 33, and James Kirby, 47,
OL,15,Fwere acting as part of the (WCK)
OL,16,Fsecurity team.
OL,18,F, were employed by the risk management
OL,19,Fcompany, Solace Global, based in Poole.
