OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FThey died alongside American-Canadian
OL,8,Fdual citizen Jacob Flickinger, 33,
OL,9,FAustralian national Lalzawmi "Zomi"
OL,10,FFrankcom, 43, who was the leader of
OL,11,Fthe relief team, Polish national
OL,12,FDamian Sobol, 35, and Palestinian
OL,13,FSaifeddin Issam Ayad Abutaha, 25.
OL,15,FThe managing director of Solace
OL,16,FGlobal, Emily Roberts, drove for more
OL,17,Fthan 12 hours to meet the after the
OL,18,Ffirm received the news.
