OL,7,FThe company's non-executive director,
OL,8,FMatthew Harding said the mood "remains
OL,9,Fprofessional but clearly raw and
OL,10,Fsaddened at what has happened".
OL,12,FHe added: "It is indeed a very sad
OL,13,Ftime. Our priority is very much the
OL,14,Fsafety of our remaining operational
OL,15,Fstaff and the families of the ones
OL,16,Fwe've lost.
