OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,F"People are clearly very upset about
OL,8,Fwhat has happened to their friends and
OL,9,Fcolleagues but they remain
OL,10,Fprofessional and focussed on the job
OL,11,Fin hand."
OL,13,FMr Harding confirmed that the Solace
OL,14,FGlobal has carried out an
OL,15,Finvestigation into the incident.
OL,17,FHe said: "We conduct meticulous risk
OL,18,Fassessments prior to mounting any
OL,19,Factivity and put in place all possible
OL,20,Frisk control measures.
