OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,F"Clearly when any incident happens,
OL,8,Fwe, as any other organisation
OL,9,Foperating in such environments, will
OL,10,Ftake a look at what happened to see if
OL,11,Fanything can be done better.
OL,13,F"We have completed a thorough
OL,14,Finvestigation into our own activities
OL,15,Fand are completely satisfied."
OL,17,FIn a statement issued through the
OL,18,FForeign Office, the family of John
OL,19,FChapman, said: "We are devastated to
OL,20,Fhave lost John, who was killed in Gaza.
